[thinking] **Considering class visibility**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about class visibility in relation to the app loader and bootstrap. If the class isn't visible to the app loader but is visible to the bootstrap, then the app loader delegates tasks to the bootstrap since everything from bootstrap is visible. I'm wondering if dynamic-access instrumentation can report by className and line, independent of the class loader. I believe the current custom copy should work if the instrumentation is active.
[thinking] 
